<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[الانشرام]</span>: انشرم الجلد: أي انشق.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">يقال:</span> شَرَمْتُ جلدَه فانشرم.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
